# Accounting Rules (V2.1)

**Authority:** `00_architecture_authority.mdc` · **Detail:** `doc/ARCHITECTURE.md` § Financial Reporting · `doc/ARCHITECTURE_V2_AGENT_RULES.md` §5

## General ledger (mandatory gateway)

**All GL writes** go through `FinancialPostingService` (`modules/accounting/services/`).

- Never write `journal_entries` / `journal_lines` from routes or domain services directly
- `JournalRepository` is used **only** from posting services / `FinancialPostingService`
- After posting: `emitFinancialPosted()` for real-time GL sync

## Posting services (reference)

| Source document | Service |
|-----------------|---------|
| Vendor bills | `billJournalPostingService` |
| Customer invoices | `invoiceJournalPostingService` |
| Bank/cash transactions | `transactionJournalPostingService` |
| Project expense vouchers | `pevJournalPostingService` |
| Investor journal | `investorJournalPostingService` |
| Fiscal period close | `fiscalPeriodCloseService` |

## Accounting periods

| Status | Behavior |
|--------|----------|
| `open` | Posting allowed |
| `closed` | Posting rejected |
| `locked` | Rejected unless `super_admin` override |

Gateway: `assertAccountingPeriodOpen` in `FinancialPostingService`.

## Shared financial core

| Package | Contents |
|---------|----------|
| `shared/financial-core/journalLedgerCore.ts` | Ledger balances, account rolls |
| `shared/financial-core/trialBalanceCore.ts` | Trial balance |
| `shared/financial-core/validation.ts` | `roundMoney`, journal validation |
| `shared/financial-core/dimensionScope.ts` | Project/building scope |
| `shared/financial-core/cashFlowJournalCore.ts` | Cash flow journal |
| `shared/financial-core/financialReconciliationEngine.ts` | Reconciliation |

Synced to `backend/src/financial/` — **do not edit generated files**. Run `npm run build:backend` after shared edits.

## Financial statements (no duplicate logic)

Balance Sheet, P&L, Cash Flow, Trial Balance, GL, subsidiary ledgers — calculations **only** in `shared/financial-core/` and `shared/report-engines/`. Prohibited in components, routes, repositories.

## Reconciliation

- Engine: `shared/financial-core/financialReconciliationEngine.ts`
- API: `modules/accounting/routes/financialReconciliationRoutes.ts`
- Certifies journal mirrors vs source documents

## Record locks

- `RecordLockRepository` + `hooks/useRecordLock.ts`
- Socket: `lock_acquired` / `lock_released`

## Journal load for reports

- `journalLedgerLoadService` — loads journal input for balance sheet / P&L
- Reports use `reportEngines/index.ts` imports

## Mutation checklist (accounting entities)

Accounts, categories, transactions, journals, periods:

1. `TenantRepository` / module service
2. `withAudit()` or `recordDomainMutation()`
3. `emitEntityEvent()` after commit
4. GL path: `FinancialPostingService` only
5. LWW where `version` column exists

## MUST NOT

- Direct GL SQL in route handlers
- Bypass period lock
- Duplicate trial balance / ledger math outside `shared/financial-core/`
- Edit `backend/src/financial/*.ts` directly
- Post journals without `emitFinancialPosted()` when clients need live GL views

## Deferred (post-launch)

Payroll → `journal_entries` unification — payroll ledger remains separate. See `ARCHITECTURE_V2_POST_LAUNCH.md`.
